OL,3,CCoroner rules medical expert 'not
OL,4,Cbiased' against Ian Paterson
OL,6,FAccusations of bias against one of the
OL,7,Fmedical experts involved in the
OL,8,Finquests into the deaths of former
OL,9,Fsurgeon Ian Paterson patients have
OL,10,Fbeen unfounded.
OL,12,FIan Paterson was jailed for 20 years
OL,13,Fin 2017 after being convicted of 20
OL,14,Fcounts of wounding.
OL,16,FMore than 60 inquests have already
OL,17,Fbeen opened into the deaths of his
OL,18,Fformer patients since July 2020.
