OL,3,CCoroner rules medical expert 'not
OL,4,Cbiased' against Ian Paterson
OL,6,FBut the disgraced former surgeon had
OL,7,Fmade claims against one of the members
OL,8,Fof the Multi-Discipliary Team, MDT, of
OL,9,Fmedical experts who are involved in
OL,10,Fthe inquests.
OL,12,FThree of them are breast surgeons and
OL,13,Ftwo are consultant oncologists.
OL,15,FIan Paterson said that emails between
OL,16,Ftwo of them showed one in particular,
OL,17,FProfessor Mike Dixon, was biased.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/8
