OL,3,CCoroner rules medical expert 'not
OL,4,Cbiased' against Ian Paterson
OL,6,FThe email included the line "we need
OL,7,Fto find someway though of exposing
OL,8,FPaterson as a liar and an incompetent
OL,9,Fsurgeon who should never have been
OL,10,Fdoing this surgery."
OL,12,FAfter considering the issue for most
OL,13,Fof January, and hearing submissions
OL,14,Ffrom various parties, the Coroner
OL,15,FRichard Foster has ruled that the
OL,16,Femail "was unfortunate, inappropriate
OL,17,Fand clumsy, although by itself it is
OL,18,Fnot indicative of actual or
OL,19,Funconscious bias."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/8
