OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe MDT team have been working on an
OL,12,Fapproach causation that the Coroner
OL,13,Fhas summarised as:
OL,15,F(a) The recurrence occurs in breast
OL,16,Ftissue which would have been removed
OL,17,Fin a properly performed mastectomy;
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/8
