OL,6,FToday, ITV News spoke to Stuart Coyne,
OL,7,Fwhose wife Catherine's death is being
OL,8,Finvestigated in the inquests.
OL,10,FHe said that he's grateful the legal
OL,11,Fargument has been resolved but finds
OL,12,Fthe time taken to discuss legal issues
OL,13,F'frustrating.' Catherine's inquest was
OL,14,Flisted for October but was rescheduled
OL,15,Fand no date yet given.
