OL,6,FStuart says "it's upsetting and
OL,7,Fdistressing because you can't really
OL,8,Fplan forwards so it affects everything
OL,9,Fof course, not only me but my family,
OL,10,Fmy son and daughter will be attending
OL,11,Fand of course all the other people who
OL,12,Fare involved in it, from the legal
OL,13,Fside to witnesses as well."
OL,15,FSome inquests are listed for final
OL,16,Fevidence next week, the first time
OL,17,Finquests have been held this year. But
OL,18,Fthe Coroner expects that this stage of
OL,19,Fthe hearings will continue into 2026.
